$ Outlook: File -> Options -> Mail -> Message arrival

The subitem *Message arrival* under the → Microsoft/Office/Outlook menu *File -> Options -> Mail* allows to enable or disable certain actions when a new message arrives:
  • Play a sound
  • Briefly change the mouse pointer
  • Shjow an envelope icon in the taskbar
  • Display a Desktop Alert
  • Enable preview for Rights Protected messages (which may impact the performance)
